hopobject.body: Could I take your name and number, please? elearning.pharmacytoday.co.nz Who cares who runs the law firm? The petty office wars are where it's at. In tonight's season premiere, a fight over Uni-ball pens and raspberry bran bars gets deliciously nasty, while Harvey's assistant, Donna (Sarah Rafferty), and his in-house nemesis, Louis (Rick Hoffman), have a scene together that would have done Jim and Dwight of "The Office" proud.
